| Command             | Description                | Key Options                      |
| ------------------- | -------------------------- | -------------------------------- |
|lscpu             | CPU architecture summary   |-p,-e,-s,-x           |
|cat /proc/cpuinfo | Detailed per-core CPU info |grep,uniq,wc -l          |
|nproc             | Number of CPU cores        |--all                          |
|top               | Real-time CPU/memory usage |-d,-p,-u                 |
|htop              | Interactive CPU monitor    |-d,-u,-p                 |
|mpstat            | CPU usage per core         |-P <CPU>,<interval> <count> |
|sar -u            | CPU usage history          |<interval> <count>,-P,-f |





